r streaming on 30 September 2014; series 2 launched in November 2014.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2014/digital/news/netflix-procures-peaky-blinders-brit-drama-in-exclusive-pact-with-weinstein-co-endemol-1201312876/ |title=Netflix Procures 'Peaky Blinders' Brit Drama in Exclusive Pact With Weinstein Co., Endemol |last=Spangler |first=Todd |date=24 September 2014 |work=Variety |accessdate=7 October 2014 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928135629/http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/netflix-procures-peaky-blinders-brit-drama-in-exclusive-pact-with-weinstein-co-endemol-1201312876/ |archive-date=28 September 2014}}</ref> Series 3 was made available 31 May 2016.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/peaky-blinders-season-3-the-british-gangland-saga-is-back-on-netflix-1464609602 |title='Peaky Blinders' Season 3: The British Gangland Saga is Back on Netflix |last=Grey |first=Tobias |date=30 May 2016 |newspaper=Wall Street Journal |issn=0099-9660 |accessdate=31 May 2016 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530125842/http://www.wsj.com/articles/peaky-blinders-season-3-the-british-gangland-saga-is-back-on-netflix-1464609602 |archive-date=30 May 2016}}</ref> Due to licensing restrictions, however, most of the show's original soundtrack is not available on the Netflix-distributed version of the series.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/peaky-blinders-10-perfectly-anachronistic-soundtrack-choices |title=10 Perfect Choices on the Peaky Blinders Soundtrack |last=Bartleet |first=Larry |date=10 May 2016 |newspaper=[[NME]] |accessdate=15 July 2016 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713134400/http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/peaky-blinders-10-perfectly-anachronistic-soundtrack-choices |archive-date=13 July 2016}}</ref> In 2018, it was announced ''Peaky Blinders'' would be moved from its original broadcast channel, [[BBC Two]], to [[BBC One]].<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/879873/Peaky-Blinders-season-5-release-date-cast-plo-When-is-the-series-released-BBC-Netflix |title=Peaky Blinders season 5 release date, cast, plot: When is the new series released? |last=Debnath |first=Neela |date=6 December 2018 |work=Daily Express |language=en |access-date=17 December 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218102051/https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/879873/Peaky-Blinders-season-5-release-date-cast-plo-When-is-the-series-released-BBC-Netflix |archive-date=18 December 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n\n[https://www.academia.edu/24202294/_Class_Place_and_History_in_the_Imaginative_Landscapes_of_Peaky_Blinders_ Long, Paul (2017) \u2018Class, Place and History in the Imaginative Landscapes of Peaky Blinders\u2019 in Forrest, D. & Johnson, B. (eds.), Social Class and Television Drama in Contemporary Britain, Palgrave]\n\n==External links==\n* {{BBC programme}}\n* {{URL|https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b045fz8r|''Peaky Blinders''}} on [[BBC]]\u2014The official website for the series in the United Kingdom.\n* {{URL|https://www.netflix.com/title/80002479|''Peaky Blinders''}} on [[Netflix]]\u2014The official website for the series in the United States.\n* {{IMDb title|id=2442560|title=Peaky Blinders}}\u2014A user-generated database of information related to the series.\n\n{{Steven Knight}}\n{{BAFTA TV Award for Best Drama Series}}\n\n{{Subject bar|portal1=Television|portal23=United Kingdom|portal2=BBC|commons=yes|commons-search=Category:Peaky Blinders (TV series)|q=yes|d=yes|d-search=Q14944179}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Peaky Blinders (Tv Series)}}\n[[Category:2010s British drama television series]]\n[[Category:2013 British television series debuts]]\n[[Category:BBC television dramas]]\n[[Category:British crime drama television series]]\n[[Category:Cultural depictions of Winston Churchill]]\n[[Category:Cultural depictions of Oswald Mosley]]\n[[