age.org/index/pdf/2017/book/index_2017.pdf|title=2017 Index of Economic Freedom|publisher=Institute for Economic Freedom|accessdate=4 February 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite web|author=The National Archives|date=11 June 2007|url=http://yourarchives.nationalarchives.gov.uk/index.php?title=Nationalisation_of_Anglo-Iranian_Oil_Company%2C_1951|title=Nationalisation of Anglo-Iranian Oil Company, 1951|publisher=The National Archives|accessdate=30 October 2011|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite web|author=New Democratic Party of Canada|date=April 2013|url=http://xfer.ndp.ca/2013/constitution/2013_CONSTITUTION_E.pdf|title=Constitution of the New Democratic Party of Canada|publisher=New Democratic Party of Canada|accessdate=9 February 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite web|author=New Democratic Party of Canada|date=February 2018|url=https://xfer.ndp.ca/2018/Documents/2018-CONSTITUTION.pdf|title=Constitution of the New Democratic Party of Canada|publisher=New Democratic Party of Canada|accessdate=9 February 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite web|author=New Zealand Labour Party|date=March 2016|url=https://www.labourparty.org.nz/sites/default/files/New%20Zealand%20%20Labour%20Party%20Policy%20Platform.pdf|title=New Zealand Labour Party Policy Platform|publisher=New Zealand Labour Party|accessdate=28 March 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite web|author=New Zealand Labour Party|date=30 November 2019|url=https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/nzlabour/pages/3956/attachments/original/1576012198/NZLP_Inc_-_Constitution___Rules_-_2019.pdf|title=New Zealand Labour Party Constitution and Rules 2019|publisher=New Zealand Labour Party|accessdate=7 January 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite web|author=New Zealand Labour Party|date=30 November 2019|url=https://www.labour.org.nz/party_info|title=Party Information|publisher=New Zealand Labour Party|accessdate=7 January 2020|ref={{harvid|New Zealand Labour Party 2019 (Party Information)}}}}\n: {{cite web|last=Noel-Schwartz|first=Heather|url=http://members.aol.com/ThryWoman/MRR.html|title=The Makhno