ystok ever.<ref>{{cite news|last=Dworza\u0144czyk|first=Tomasz|title=Jagiellonia Bia\u0142ystok: Adam D\u017awiga\u0142a zosta\u0142 najm\u0142odszym strzelcem|url=http://www.poranny.pl/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20130305/EKSTRAKLASA/130309798|accessdate=6 March 2013|newspaper=Kurier Poranny|date=5 March 2013|language=Polish}}<br>- {{cite web |url=http://www.90minut.pl/news/278/news2786964-Adam-Dzwigala-w-Wisle-Plock.html |title=Adam D\u017awiga\u0142a w Wi\u015ble P\u0142ock |publisher= |website=90minut |date=28 June 2017 |accessdate=28 June 2017 |language=Polish}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{WorldFootball.net|adam-dzwigala}}\n* {{90minut|21465}}\n* {{Soccerway|adam-dwigaa/258193}}\n\n{{C.D. Aves squad}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2013}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dzwigala, Adam}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Warsaw]]\n[[Category:Polish footballers]]\n[[Category:Polish expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Poland under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Ekstraklasa players]]\n[[Category:Primeira Liga players]]\n[[Category:\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a players]]\n[[Category:Jagiellonia Bia\u0142ystok players]]\n[[Category:Lechia Gda\u0144sk players]]\n[[Category:G\u00f3rnik Zabrze players]]\n[[Category:G\u00f3rnik \u0141\u0119czna players]]\n[[Category:Wis\u0142a P\u0142ock players]]\n[[Category:C.D. Aves players]]\n[[Category:Polish expatriate sportspeople in Portugal]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Portugal]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Polish footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Adam D\u017awiga\u0142a\n| fullname    = Adam D\u017awiga\u0142a\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1995|09|25|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[Warsaw]], [[Poland]]\n| height      = {{convert|1.82|m|abbr=on}}\n| position    = [[Defender (association football)|Centre back]]\n| currentclub = [[C.D. Aves|Aves]]\n| clubnumbe